def dig(a):
    c=0
    i=a
    while i>0:
        c=c+1
        i=i//10
    
    return c
def sums(a,b):
    s=0
    i=a
    while i>0:
        s=s+pow(i%10,b)
        i=i//10
    return s

import math
for _ in range(int(input())):
    N = int(input())

    T = N
    R = 0
    while(T>0):
        M = T%10
        T = T//10
        R += pow(M, D)
    
    if R == N:
